title: IModelDoc2.EditUnsuppressDependent2
description: Unsuppresses the selected feature or component and their dependents.
returns: True if the selected feature or component and their dependents are unsuppressed, false if not
remarks: This method is identical to the obsoleted IModelDoc2::EditUnsuppressDependent method. The version number was incremented to allow Visual Basic applications to take advantage of information not available in the obsoleted IPartDoc::EditUnsuppressDependent method.
